ITEM NO.53               COURT NO.11               SECTION II
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
SPECIAL LEAVE PETITION (CRIMINAL) Diary No. 31382/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated 17-09-2024
in SBCRMBA No. 825/2024 passed by the High Court of Judicature for
Rajasthan at Jaipur]
SANTOSH KUMAR SHARMA & ANR.                        Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
STATE OF RAJASTHAN                                 Respondent(s)
(IA No. 152699/2025 - CONDONATION OF DELAY IN FILING and IA No.
152701/2025 - EXEMPTION FROM FILING O.T.)
 
Date : 04-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE M.M. SUNDRESH
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE K. VINOD CHANDRAN
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s) : 
                   Mr. Col. Bala Subramanian, Sr. Adv.
                   Mr. Sarthak Chaturvedi, Adv.
                   Mr. Vaibhav Maheshwari, Adv.
                   Ms. Pritee Singh, Adv.
                   Ms. Dimple Sirohi, Adv.
                   Mr. Mohan Shyam Sharma, Adv.
                   Mr. Sriram P., AOR
                                      
For Respondent(s) : 
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
1) List on 08th July, 2025. 
2) In the meanwhile, the petitioner shall implead the
complainant as a party. 
(NIDHI AHUJA)                    (POONAM VAID)
